**Explanation for `index.html`:**
*   Links to `style.css` and `script.js`.
*   Includes `socket.io.js` (client-side library) and `jQuery` (for easier DOM manipulation).
*   `username-section`: Contains the input and button for choosing a username. Initially visible.
*   `chat-app`: Contains the main chat interface (sidebar for users, message display, message input). Initially hidden (`hidden` class).
*   `messages` div: Where new chat messages will be appended.
*   `user-list` ul: Where the list of connected users will be displayed.

